          <p>Chat with Claude, Codex, or Gemini. Watch them work in real-time through the monitoring interface.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="workflow-connector"></div>

      <div class="workflow-step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Review and commit</h3>
          <p>See all changes in the diff viewer. Stage what you want, commit when ready, and push to remote.</p>
